with puttin' the fear of God
in your heart.

28:23.876 --> 28:25.584
Oh, is that right?

28:25.668 --> 28:28.084
So you gonna go
Old Testament on me, J.D.?

28:29.793 --> 28:33.292
The kid stays a Buckeye...

28:34.918 --> 28:37.459
